# Paddle game

Paddle game is a JavaScript game built using the latest HTML canvas API technologies, to create an interactive animation.

## How to get the project

First, download the file from GitHub and start it on a local server.



## Usage

```
User the space bar key to start the game

Use the arrow keys to move the paddle to the right or to the left.

You can also choose the level you want to play, the game consist of 3 levels.
```

## WIN OR LOSE
You can win by killing all the spaceships.
You might lose the game in case the ball goes outside the paddle or the spaceship classes the world borders.

